{"tid":533713,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"SSD與HDD輕鬆合體 AMD推出Enmotus FuzeDrive for Ryzen硬碟混合軟體","createTime":"2018-01-19T05:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T17:19:25.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6aedc360868d6ff827478a5441964f22881181ec","tid":533713,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.mobile01.com/newsdetail/23793/amd-enmotus-fuzedrive-for-ryzen-ssd-hdd-intel-optane-memory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobile01.com%2Fnewsdetail%2F23793%2Famd-enmotus-fuzedrive-for-ryzen-ssd-hdd-intel-optane-memory&d=Q26sThRywBPecVqUHaKi6J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b413fbe1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mobile01.com/newsdetail/23793/amd-enmotus-fuzedrive-for-ryzen-ssd-hdd-intel-optane-memory</a><br />\n<br />\nAMD近來與Enmotus軟體公司合作推出一款專為AMD Ryzen平台所設計的Enmotus FuzeDrive For AMD Ryzen軟體，主要特色是可以將小容量的SSD固態硬碟與容量較大的HDD硬碟結合成一個vSSD虛擬固態儲存磁區，好讓這個vSSD磁區不僅可達到SSD的傳輸速度，也同時具有HDD硬碟的大容量規格，就跟Intel推出的Optane Memory用法有點類似，簡單來說就是透過軟體讓SSD與HDD變成一個混合式硬碟使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201801/mobile01-3955beee68a236866994aade00125004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2Fattach%2F201801%2Fmobile01-3955beee68a236866994aade00125004.jpg&h=ea99bb49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就AMD提供的資料來看，透過這個軟體來結合SSD與HDD之後，傳輸效能都有明顯提升。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201801/mobile01-307d6b06e921a21a0f499bde178bd76a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2Fattach%2F201801%2Fmobile01-307d6b06e921a21a0f499bde178bd76a.jpg&h=05479ede&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"bdd2b12cd3aa7712f961353c7d4688635a016856","tid":533713,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 只要是使用AMD X399、X370或是B350等主機板平台都可以使用這款專為AMD Ryzen平台推出的Enmotus FuzeDrive，並可支援SSD+HDD、NVMe SSD+SSD或是Optane SSD+SSD或HDD等硬碟搭配組合，不過用來當作加速快取的SSD部分目前就只有支援至128GB的容量，而作為主要儲存空間的硬碟則是可以支援至10TB容量。Enmotus FuzeDrive For AMD Ryzen軟體已經在官方網站開賣，售價是美金19.99元，要是手邊AMD Ryzen平台又有這類需求的話，不妨可以參考看看囉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201801/mobile01-86804d65c748c21d98fcff969a48fadb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2Fattach%2F201801%2Fmobile01-86804d65c748c21d98fcff969a48fadb.jpg&h=ae74bfd0&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1773ad5a1139fe7579c951c281826be06cf35247","tid":533713,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"AMD 表示， FuzeDrive 可讓 Windows 系統的啟動速度加快 172%，而啟動其他程式則可加速達 9.3 倍，載入遊戲的速度也大幅加快。FuzeDrive 分兩個版本，基本版定價為 19.99 美元 ( 約港幣HK$157 )，而進階版則售 59.99 美元 ( 約港幣HK$470 )，現已在 Enmotus 的網站上發售。<br />\n<br />\n基本版: FuzeDrive Basic <br />\n用於加速用的優先SSD 最高容量 128GB<br />\n支援NVMe 與 SAS/SATA SSD<br />\n2GB FuzeRAM<br />\n價格 US$19.99( 約港幣HK$157 )<br />\n<br />\n進階版: FuzeDrive Plus<br />\n用於加速用的優先SSD 最高容量 1TB<br />\n支援NVMe 與 SAS/SATA SSD<br />\n4GB FuzeRAM<br />\n價格 US$59.99( 約港幣HK$470 )<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/01/18/fuzedrive/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2Ffuzedrive%2Fnotebook%2F&d=Q26sThRywBPecVqUHaKi6J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=314e7f10\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/01/18/fuzedrive/notebook/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.enmotus.com/amd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.enmotus.com%2Famd&d=Q26sThRywBPecVqUHaKi6J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=65f395de\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.enmotus.com/amd</a>"},{"pid":"fc6c753c9d3fef59d013b1c1093c0738f17ecb07","tid":533713,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"有pcie ssd不用買呢D軟件 <br />\n佢只是 amd version optana"},{"pid":"800740e4476c4d8fa8890cf0a041f59be5e9f421","tid":533713,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc6c753c9d3fef59d013b1c1093c0738f17ecb07","tid":533713,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"有pcie ssd不用買呢D軟件 <br />\n佢只是 amd version optana"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"???"},{"pid":"34bea5ab14e27cd1e6fb2871556a26437b26bf58","tid":533713,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"800740e4476c4d8fa8890cf0a041f59be5e9f421","tid":533713,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc6c753c9d3fef59d013b1c1093c0738f17ecb07","tid":533713,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"有pcie ssd不用買呢D軟件 <br />\n佢只是 amd version optana"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"amd版SRT/fusion drive/SSHD"},{"pid":"716a357238a79b662877812733a07c70528e96c7","tid":533713,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"你當係要俾錢既普通軟件算"},{"pid":"fe3c5d9ae13061d7040ad5beeb52968441512475","tid":533713,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得用家都係極端，好少人會再有心機將ssd同hdd炒埋一碟"}]}